正常常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人都有類似問題？點解會咁？ ？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 每個禮拜換一次枕頭套，應該唔關事</blockquote><br />\n你係咪有打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打丁會出頭油，你自己渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb034447e24124cd382befff42c91d97c459857","tid":627071,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9d94b26406df082371996ba871514d7ed6561e","tid":627071,"uid":129521,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T17:46:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚先會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"Sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c19823abf335b941770370db20d23e8ba623029","tid":627071,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a91b913e794812a178337a0463d1a14f0419668a","tid":627071,"uid":34084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T17:48:43.000Z","msg":"試下用dry shampoo啦 可以幫你節省好多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇吓"},{"pid":"cc0dae83d0a72d7a6c29b3d7a6a94f897d59efcf","tid":627071,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T01:31:55.000Z","msg":"乜唔係正常人訓醒個頭都會油架咩？"},{"pid":"16addb6f3f9766745888c219879125e6edb534b9","tid":627071,"uid":43106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"你要轉洗頭水"},{"pid":"504db64826ae9876d0f5a41e3e1718104dfcb690","tid":627071,"uid":2114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"一星期用一次selsun blue<br />\n唔得嘅就升級上去用selsun super<br />\n包你有好大改善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde2e37a3b390f52fb2ca2